gnuefi
======

Prerequisites to build:
----------------------
- gnu-efi headers

- gnu-efi libs:
    libefi.a
    libgnuefi.a

- other dependency:
    crt0-efi-$(ARCH).o
    elf_$(ARCH)_efi.lds

- Update paths of above prerequisites to Makefile variables
  EFIINC, EFILIB, LIB

To build gnu-efi from sources:

 $ git clone https://git.code.sf.net/p/gnu-efi/code gnu-efi
 $ cd gnu-efi
 $ make

To install gnu-efi and headers on CentOS:

 $ sudo yum install gnu-efi gnu-efi-devel

